resources.string: All online courses are free of cost\n\n
You can study any time you want. Online courses give you the flexibility to spend time with work, family, friends, significant others or any other activity you like.\n\n
Because you have a direct pipeline to the instructor via e-mail, you can get your questions answered directly.\n\n
When you complete this course, you will be able to include e-mail and web browsing as technical skills on your resume.\n\n
